@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_rsytcz(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.46) - 0.33) / (wp.sin(tmp + 0.38) / (v2 + 0.82 + v2 + 0.50)))
    v0 = ((wp.sin(tmp + 0.60) - (tmp + 0.72 - v1 + 0.91)) + 0.95)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v0 + 0.19) + (v2 + 0.32 * v2 + 0.75)) / wp.abs(wp.abs(v0 + 0.29)))
    v0 = (wp.exp(wp.abs(v1 + 0.84)) * wp.abs(v2))
    data[tid] = v0
